the gift certificates.

08:14.682 --> 08:15.725
Oh, man.

08:15.725 --> 08:17.359
I'm gonna call Emilio
and tell him

08:17.359 --> 08:18.864
to short-sheet him
on the crotch.

08:18.864 --> 08:20.367
You are bad at this, dude.

08:20.367 --> 08:22.574
Oh, whatever, Robin.

08:22.574 --> 08:24.779
Like you've ever
talked your way out of a ticket.

08:24.779 --> 08:26.113
Are you kidding me?

08:26.113 --> 08:27.185
Robin's a pretty girl.

08:27.185 --> 08:28.359
Pretty girls don't get tickets.

08:28.359 --> 08:30.324
I bet Robin's been
pulled over tons of times,

08:30.324 --> 08:31.397
never once gotten a ticket.

08:31.397 --> 08:34.134
